### **4. 27_StreamViewScope**  
**Description:**  
Displays live numeric input as a real-time scrolling chart with adjustable speed.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# StreamViewScope - Live Metric Chart Renderer

StreamViewScope visualizes fast-moving numeric data with clean charts ideal for dashboards or simulations.

## Features
- Scrollable real-time line chart  
- Adjustable refresh interval  
- Lightweight and responsive  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/27_StreamViewScope.git
cd 27_StreamViewScope
python visualize.py
